	(9907,'sb_we_settings','O:8:\"stdClass\":14:{s:17:\"header_from_email\";s:37:\"investorrelations@fourpointenergy.com\";s:16:\"header_from_name\";s:16:\"FourPoint Energy\";s:14:\"header_send_as\";s:4:\"html\";s:18:\"set_global_headers\";s:1:\"1\";s:12:\"user_subject\";s:29:\"[[blog_name]] Investor Update\";s:9:\"user_body\";s:1279:\"FourPoint Energy Investor,\r\n<br /><br />\r\nAs part of our newly launched website FourPoint has a specific Investor section that allows you secure access to quarterly and annual reports, capital call notices and relevant company presentations.  You may access this information by visiting the investor section on our website and logging in using the provided user name and password.  Please note, the password provided is a randomly generated password that should be changed immediately.  Please follow the instructions below for resetting your password. \r\n<br /><br />\r\nUsername: [user_login]<br /><br />Password: [reset_pass_link]<br /><br />\r\n<br /><br />\r\nInstructions to change your password:\r\n<br /><br />\r\n          1. Click \"Investors\" in the main navigation.<br /><br />\r\n          2. Click \"Forgot Password?\".<br /><br />\r\n          3. Enter your email address and click \"Get New Password\".<br /><br />\r\n          4. You\'ll receive an email from FourPoint Energy. <br /><br />\r\n          5. Follow the instructions to reset your password.<br /><br />\r\n <br /><br />\r\nThank you and should you have any questions or issue with your login please contact Jenna Samek at jsamek@fourpointenergy.com.\r\n<br /><br />\r\nBest Regards,\r\n<br /><br />\r\nFourPoint Investor Relations Team\";s:17:\"we_attachment_url\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"header_additional\";s:0:\"\";s:15:\"header_reply_to\";s:26:\"jsamek@fourpointenergy.com\";s:13:\"admin_subject\";s:35:\"[[blog_name]] New User Registration\";s:10:\"admin_body\";s:105:\"New user registration on your blog [blog_name]<br /><br />Username: [user_login]<br />Email: [user_email]\";s:2