	(1401,231,'_timeline_items_0_timeline_year','field_56fab9c610702'),
	(1402,231,'timeline_items_0_timeline_description','Cordillera Energy Partners was founded in February 2000 and incorporated as a Limited Liability Company formed in the state of Texas. The Company formed by George Solich, President and CEO, and his management team, employed the âacquire/exploitâ strategyâbuying producing assets and underdeveloped assets in two or three core areas. They enhanced production, cash flow, and reserves through a combination of drilling and lowering the cost structure, while adding additional âbolt-onâ acquisitions.'),
	(1403,231,'_timeline_items_0_timeline_description','field_56fab9e210703'),
