	(1431,231,'_timeline_items_5_timeline_year','field_56fab9c610702'),
	(1432,231,'timeline_items_5_timeline_description','CEP III held assets and operations in the Texas Panhandle, Western Oklahoma, and the East Texas Basin. In 2010 Cordillera celebrated its 10th year in business and made plans to form its fourth enterprise centered around the âacquire/exploitâ strategy. During this period, the Cordillera management team executed on both small and large producing property and acreage acquisitions totaling over $700 million and has drilled over 235 wells (vertical and horizontal) investing over $300 million.'),
