	(2838,445,'profile_bio_summary','Jacob Shumway joined FourPoint Energy in March of 2014, as the Vice President of Engineering.'),
	(2839,445,'_profile_bio_summary','field_56fac0aba3463'),
	(2840,445,'profile_bio','Shumway\'s responsibilities cover the reservoir engineering functions at FourPoint including reservoir modeling, development planning, evaluation of business development opportunities and corporate reserves. Shumway holds a Bachelor of Science in Petroleum Engineering from the Colorado School of Mines. He is also a member of the Society of Petroleum Engineers and is a Licensed Professional Engineer in the State of Colorado.'),
