	(2861,447,'_profile_thumbnail','field_56faca5beb654'),
	(2862,447,'profile_bio_summary','Tony Cristelli joined FourPoint Energy in April 2014 as Vice President of Land.'),
	(2863,447,'_profile_bio_summary','field_56fac0aba3463'),
	(2864,447,'profile_bio','Prior to joining FourPoint, Cristelli served in various capacities for Cimarex Energy Co., beginning in 2005 as a Regional Landman, followed by an appointment to Mid-Continent Region Land Manager in 2007, and most recently Mid-Continent Region Manager in April 2012. He began his career in 2002 with Chesapeake Energy Corporation in its Acquisitions and Divestitures group. Cristelli holds a Bachelor of Science in Finance from the University of Oklahoma.'),
