	(3707,532,'page_description','After you build three successful energy exploration companies in 12 years, the only thing left to do is start a fourth. FourPoint Energy is a new oil and gas exploration and production company founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy. With over 30 years of industry leadership, FourPoint Energy seeks to develop our most valuable resource, opportunity.Â  \r\n'),
