	(3929,559,'_edit_lock','1461190285:1'),
	(3948,563,'page_description','FourPoint Energy is headquartered in Denver, Colorado with field offices in Woodward, Oklahoma, Elk City, Oklahoma and Borger, Texas. Geographically focused in the Anadarko and Permian Basins, the company targets low risk repeatable stacked multi-pay resource plays.\r\n\r\nFrom the shallow zones like the Douglas and Tonkawa, to the deeper Granite Wash, Missourian Wash and Morrow, there are a total of 27 established producing resources in one of the most prolific hydrocarbon producing basins in the world. With FourPoint\'s long history and technical expertise in the area, these plays can provide repeatable long-lived resources with significant growth potential.\r\n\r\nThe Permian, similar in nature has 23 multiple stacked horizontal targets.'),
