	(5383,65,'timeline_items_10_timeline_description','In February, FourPoint announced the acquisition of all of the remaining Chesapeake Exploration, L.L.C. assets in the Western Anadarko Basin for $385 million. These assets included interest in 3,500 wells producing a combined 260 Mmcfed and 473,000 net acres with a significant inventory of undeveloped locations. To finance this acquisition, FourPoint issued $600 million of equity and expanded its borrowing base with its commercial bank group.'),
