	(7471,795,'page_description','After building three successful energy companies in 12 years, the only thing left to do was to start a fourth. FourPoint Energy is an exploration and production company founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy Partners. With over 30 years of industry leadership, FourPoint has a history to support its future growth to seek its greatest untapped resource: Opportunity.'),
