	(11276,1296,'profile_bio','Marvin is responsible for origination, analysis, execution and integration of acquisitions as well as execution of divestitures. Prior to joining FourPoint Energy, Marvin was a Partner with Petrie Partners and a Vice President with Bank of America Merrill Lynchâs Energy Investment Banking Group. Before his investment banking career, he was a Field Artillery Captain in the U.S. Armyâs 25th Infantry Division. Marvin earned a Bachelor of Science from the United States Military Academy at West Point, an MBA from Georgetown University and is a CFA Charterholder.'),
