	(349,3,'2016-04-06 17:05:32','2016-04-06 17:05:32','<img src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"auto\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-343\" />\r\n<h3>Why lease or sell to FourPoint Energy?</h3>\r\n<h4>Aggressive Offers</h4>\r\nWe pay at or above market based terms and are experienced to move quickly on simple or complex trades.\r\n<h4>Defined Areas of Focus:</h4>\r\nOur leasing is focused on areas where FourPoint actively drills and operates.\r\n<h4>Active Developer</h4>\r\nWe are not an asset warehouse. Our business strategy employs an acquisition development model that accelerates the pace of value creation.\r\n<h4>Financial Strength</h4>\r\nAs a privately funded company, we have a strong balance sheet with over $2.5 billion of committed capital and backing from some of the largest funds in private equity.\r\n<h4>Highly Experienced Team:</h4>\r\nOur team of engineers, geologists, landman and other professionals have a strong experience base. We are committed to capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking, and strategic relationships. This translates to being able to execute on leasing, drilling and acquisitions in the most efficient and effective manner.\r\n<h4>Experienced Vertical and Horizontal Driller:</h4>\r\nWe have a dedicated team of drilling and completion engineers as well as development geologists that have drilled and completed over 320 operated wells in the last 16 years with nearly 200 of those in the modern horizontal environment.\r\n<h4>Active Producing Property Buyer:</h4>\r\nWith over 30 years of demonstrated acquisition experience to evaluate and pay for producing and undeveloped reserves, FourPoint has closed over ___ acquisition transactions ranging in size from less than $1 million to $1 Billion.\r\n<h4>Responsible Operator:</h4>\r\nWe are a prudent, responsible, low cost operator. We have a disciplined approach to efficiency and cost reduction. Our technical team is highly experienced in drilling and completions in both horizontal and vertical wells. We are committed to the safe and environmentally responsible development of our energy resources and invest time and resources to improve the communities in which we live and work.\r\n<h4>Relationship Driven:</h4>\r\nOur acquisition strategy incorporates a win-win philosophy to deal making. We strive to build long-term relationships and partnerships that stimulate additional transactions down the road.\r\n<h4>Farmouts and Joint-Ventures:</h4>\r\nWe encourage owners to provide us the opportunity to accelerate the development of their acreage via farmout or joint-venture agreements.\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Leasing:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Scott Haselwood</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Senior Land Advisor, Manager of Leasing\r\n(303) 785-1547 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 720-877-1564 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Asset Sales:</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brad Marvin</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vice President, Business Development\r\n(303) 785-1554 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 974-0275 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Main areas of focus for leasing and asset acquisitions</h3>\r\n<h4>Active Plays</h4>\r\nWestern Anadarko Basin: Texas Panhandle &amp; Western Oklahoma\r\n<h4>Areas of Focus</h4>\r\n<strong>New Mexico:</strong>\r\n\r\nLea, Eddy\r\n\r\n<strong>Texas:</strong>\r\n\r\nLoving, Culberson, Winkler, Ward, Reeves, Martin, Howard, Glasscock, Midland, Upton, Reagan\r\nOperating Counties\r\n\r\n<strong>Texas