	(475,2,'2016-04-18 21:29:50','2016-04-18 21:29:50','At FourPoint, our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. Check out how your opportunities can grow alongside ours. To view all of our current openings and to apply, please <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent privately owned exploration and production company based in Denver, Colorado with a field office in Woodward, Oklahoma. We are committed to creating value that makes a difference by practicing and living out our values (hyperlink) that define us as an organization.','Join Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','218-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 21:29:50','2016-04-18 21:29:50','',218,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/218-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(476,2,'2016-04-18 21:30:52','2016-04-18 21:30:52','Building on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies over the last 15 years, you can expect our team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decision with a sense of urgency. Although our name has changed, FourPoint Energy possesses the same passion for creating value for our shareholders, the same commitment to working âBetter, Smarter, Fasterâ, and the same dedication to community stewardship.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team moving across all functional areas we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and executing our plan. Since the companyâs inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-quality equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance and partnership with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. The goal is to be the buyer of choice, lessee of choice, driller of choice, investment of choice, employer of choice, and eventually, seller of choice. We consider ourselves âEnergy Farmersâ and respect the land and its opportunity for multiple uses.\r\n\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Our Values:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Shared Vision â Creating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.</li>\r\n	<li>Committed Teamwork â Fostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.</li>\r\n	<li>Empowering People â Entrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.</li>\r\n	<li>Driven to Excellence â Committing to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.</li>\r\n	<li>Entrepreneurial â capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.</li>\r\n	<li>Compassionate Stewardship â positively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.</li>\r\n</ul>','Company Culture','','inherit','closed','closed','','221-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 21:30:52','2016-04-18 21:30:52','',221,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(477,2,'2016-04-18 21:31:22','2016-04-18 21:31:22','FourPoint Energy is proud to offer its employees a top-of-the-line benefits program, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Medical Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Dental Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Life and Long-Term Disability Insurance</li>\r\n	<li>Paid Sick Leave</li>\r\n	<li>Paid Holidays</li>\r\n	<li>401k with Employer Match</li>\r\n	<li>Annual Bonus Potential</li>\r\n	<li>4 1/2 Day Workweek</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nEmployees can take advantage of vacation time tied to industry experience, and what we fondly call âebb timeâ after weâve successfully completed a significant acquisition or transaction. Employees have used this time, which doesnât count toward vacation time, to take long awaited family vacations, go on mission trips, work on home projects, and do community service.\r\n\r\nAnd the best part? Everyone shares in the companyâs financial success. Employees receive a considerable portion of their compensation through performance-based incentives, including equity ownership.','Benefits & Compensation','','inherit','closed','closed','','224-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 21:31:22','2016-04-18 21:31:22','',224,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/224-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(478,2,'2016-04-18 21:31:53','2016-04-18 21:31:53','FourPoint provides hands-on training for interns, who may work in the following Departments:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Accounting</li>\r\n	<li>Land</li>\r\n	<li>Geology</li>\r\n	<li>Reservoir and Production Engineering</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nTo view all of our current intern program openings and to apply, please <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com\" target=\"_blank\">click here</a>.\r\n\r\nFourPoint summer interns have represented the following universities:\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Arizona State University</li>\r\n	<li>Colorado School of Mines</li>\r\n	<li>Colorado State University</li>\r\n	<li>Duke University</li>\r\n	<li>Metropolitan State College of Denver</li>\r\n	<li>University of Colorado</li>\r\n	<li>University of Kansas</li>\r\n	<li>University of Wyoming</li>\r\n	<li>Western State University</li>\r\n	<li>Princeton University An Equal Opportunity Employer</li>\r\n</ul>','Internship Program','','inherit','closed','closed','','227-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 21:31:53','2016-04-18 21:31:53','',227,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/227-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(479,2,'2016-04-18 21:32:57','2016-04-18 21:32:57','<h3>Why lease or sell to FourPoint Energy?</h3>\r\n<h4><img class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-356\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo300x300.png\" alt=\"fpo300x300\" width=\"300\" height=\"300\" />Aggressive Offers</h4>\r\nWe pay at or above market based terms and are experienced to move quickly on simple or complex trades.\r\n<h4>Defined Areas of Focus</h4>\r\nOur leasing is focused on areas where FourPoint actively drills and operates.\r\n<h4>Active Developer</h4>\r\nWe are not an asset warehouse. Our business strategy employs an acquisition development model that accelerates the pace of value creation.\r\n<h4>Financial Strength</h4>\r\nAs a privately funded company, we have a strong balance sheet with over $2.5 billion of committed capital and backing from some of the largest funds in private equity.\r\n<h4>Highly Experienced Team</h4>\r\nOur team of engineers, geologists, landman and other professionals have a strong experience base. We are committed to capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking, and strategic relationships. This translates to being able to execute on leasing, drilling and acquisitions in the most efficient and effective manner.\r\n<h4>Experienced Vertical and Horizontal Driller</h4>\r\nWe have a dedicated team of drilling and completion engineers as well as development geologists that have drilled and completed over 320 operated wells in the last 16 years with nearly 200 of those in the modern horizontal environment.\r\n<h4>Active Producing Property Buyer</h4>\r\nWith over 30 years of demonstrated acquisition experience to evaluate and pay for producing and undeveloped reserves, FourPoint has closed over ___ acquisition transactions ranging in size from less than $1 million to $1 Billion.\r\n<h4>Responsible Operator</h4>\r\nWe are a prudent, responsible, low cost operator. We have a disciplined approach to efficiency and cost reduction. Our technical team is highly experienced in drilling and completions in both horizontal and vertical wells. We are committed to the safe and environmentally responsible development of our energy resources and invest time and resources to improve the communities in which we live and work.\r\n<h4>Relationship Driven</h4>\r\nOur acquisition strategy incorporates a win-win philosophy to deal making. We strive to build long-term relationships and partnerships that stimulate additional transactions down the road.\r\n<h4>Farmouts and Joint-Ventures</h4>\r\nWe encourage owners to provide us the opportunity to accelerate the development of their acreage via farmout or joint-venture agreements.\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Leasing</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Scott Haselwood</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Senior Land Advisor, Manager of Leasing\r\n(303) 785-1547 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 720-877-1564 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">shaselwood@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"opp-contact\">\r\n<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Contact for Asset Sales</h3>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Brad Marvin</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Vice President, Business Development\r\n(303) 785-1554 (direct)\r\n(303) 290-9997 (fax)\r\n(303) 974-0275 (cell)\r\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">bmarvin@fourpointenergy.com</u></a></p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>Main areas of focus for leasing and asset acquisitions</h3>\r\n<h4 class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\">Active Plays:Â </span></h4>\r\n<p class=\"p1\"><span class=\"s1\"><strong>Western Anadarko Basin:</strong> Texas Panhandle &amp; Western Oklahoma</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h4>Areas of Focus:</h4>\r\n<strong>New Mexico:Â </strong>Lea and Eddy\r\n\r\n<strong>Texas:Â </strong>Loving, Culberson, Winkler, Ward, Reeves, Martin, Howard, Glasscock, Midland, Upton, Reagan andÂ Operating Counties\r\n\r\n<strong>Texas:Â </strong>Hansford, Hemphill, Hutchinson, Lipscomb, Ochiltree, Roberts and Wheeler\r\n\r\n<strong>Oklahoma:Â </strong>Beckham, Blaine, Caddo, Canadian, Cleveland, Comanche, Custer, Dewey, Ellis, Garvin, Grady, McClain, Roger Mills, Washita and Woodward','Business Opportunities','','inherit','closed','closed','','71-revision-v1','','','2016-04-18 21:32:57','2016-04-18 21:32:57','',71,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/04/18/71-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
