	(664,2,'2016-04-29 17:00:52','2016-04-29 17:00:52','<img class=\"size-full wp-image-342 alignright\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo450x450.png\" alt=\"fpo450x450\" width=\"450\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nFourPoint is primarily focused on acquiring and developing oil and natural gas assets in the Western Anadarko and Permian Basins. Founded by the leadership team of Cordillera Energy Partners following the sale to Apache Corporation in 2012, FourPoint Energy is proud to boast an exceptional team of professionals with over 30 years of industry-leading experience.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is committed to our mission of <strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\"><em data-redactor-tag=\"em\">creating value that makes a difference</em></strong>. We strive to do this every day and in every part of the organization by fostering relationships with our investors, partners, land and mineral owners, vendors and employees with the highest level of respect and integrity. We are focused on continuous improvement through collaboration and innovation but also emphasize processes to maximize efficiencies.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is very proud of the culture and environment it has developed over the years. We are a dedicated team of individuals committed to carrying out our mission through six core values:\r\n<h3>Driven to Excellence</h3>\r\nCommitting to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.\r\n<h3>Entrepreneurial</h3>\r\nCapturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.\r\n<h3>Empowering People</h3>\r\nEntrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.\r\n<h3>Committed Teamwork</h3>\r\nFostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.\r\n<h3>Shared Vision</h3>\r\nC