	(687,2,'2016-06-09 17:10:17','2016-06-09 17:10:17','This list provides the documentation FourPoint Energy will need in order to complete the change to your ownership account. All change requests must be submitted in writing.\n\nShould you have any additional questions regarding the documentation required to complete a change to your account, please feel free to contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</a>\n<h3><strong>Address Change</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li><a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/ADDRESS-VERIFICATION_CHANGE-FORM-2016.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">Submit request in writing</a> with your signature</li>\n 	<li>New <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Appointment of Attorney-In-Fact</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Copy of Power of Attorney</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Bankruptcy â Chapter 7</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Recorded conveyance (if applicable)</li>\n 	<li>Order naming trustee of bankruptcy estate</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Bankruptcy â Chapter 11</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Plan of reorganization</li>\n 	<li>Order confirming the plan of reorganization</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Changes in Trustee</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Instrument by which the Successor Trustee was appointed</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Company Name Change</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Certificate of NameÂ Change including Tax I.D.</li>\n 	<li>New <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9Â </a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Change Due to Merger</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Certificate of Merger including Tax I.D.</li>\n 	<li>New <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Death of owner with a will with probate proceedings conducted in the state where the property is located</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Death Certificate</li>\n 	<li>Letters testamentary</li>\n 	<li>Final decree of distribution or judgment of possession</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Death of owner with a will with probate proceedings conducted outside the state where the property is located</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Death Certificate</li>\n 	<li>Letters testamentary</li>\n 	<li>Final decree of distribution or judgment of possession recorded in the county where the property is located</li>\n 	<li>Documentation of ancillary probate proceedings opened in all affected states</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Death of owner without a will</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Death Certificate</li>\n 	<li>Letters of administration</li>\n 	<li>Final decree of distribution or judgment of possession recorded in the county where the property is located</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Enroll or change in revenue direct deposit</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Submit <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_DirectDepositEnrollment2016-with-mailing-info.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">new direct deposit form</a> with voided check</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Joint Tenancy with Death of One Tenant</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Death Certificate of deceased tenant Life Estate â Death</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Life tenantâs Death Certificate</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Names and addresses of remaindermen</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Name Change</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Marriage Certificate or Divorce Decree reinstating maiden name or other legal document of name change</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Ownership Change Due to Divorce</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Complete Divorce Decree including Settlement Agreement and recorded conveyances (if applicable)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Sale of Interest</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Complete copy of conveyance document filed of record in the county which the property is located</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Trust or Partnership Creation or Dissolution</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n 	<li>Trust or Partnership Agreement and recorded conveyance(s) (if applicable)</li>\n</ul>\n<strong><em>Legal Advice</em></strong>\n\nFourPoint Energy is unable to provide legal advice. Please contact an attorney for any questions regarding legal advice.\n\n<strong><em>IRS Form W-9</em></strong>\n\nFederal law requires all owners to provide their social security number or tax identification number via an IRS Form <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9</a>. Should you fail to provide this information, you may become subject to non-refundable backup withholding.','Change of Ownership','','inherit','closed','closed','','197-autosave-v1','','','2016-06-09 17:10:17','2016-06-09 17:10:17','',197,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/02/197-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(688,2,'2016-05-02 17:43:42','2016-05-02 17:43:42','To help assist you with your request to make a change to your ownership account, we have provided a list of situations and occurrences that require changes be made to your account. The list provides the documentation FourPoint Energy will need in order to complete the change to your ownership account. All change requests must be submitted in writing.\r\n\r\nShould you have any additional questions regarding the documentation required to complete a change to your account, please feel free to contact us at (303) 785-1581 or <a href=\"mailto:ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com\"><u data-redactor-tag=\"u\">ownerrelations@fourpointenergy.com</u></a>\r\n<h3>Address Change</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Submit request in writing with your signature</li>\r\n 	<li>New W-9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Appointment of Attorney-In-Fact</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Copy of Power of Attorney</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Bankruptcy - Chapter 7</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Recorded conveyance (if applicable)</li>\r\n 	<li>Order naming trustee of bankruptcy estate</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Bankruptcy - Chapter 11</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Plan of reorganization</li>\r\n 	<li>Order confirming the plan of reorganization</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Changes in Trustee</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Instrument by which the Successor Trustee was appointed</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Company Name Change</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Certificate of NameÂ Change including Tax I.D.</li>\r\n 	<li>New W-9 Company Name</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Change Due to Merger</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Certificate of Merger including Tax I.D.</li>\r\n 	<li>New W-9</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Death of owner with a will that has not been probated</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Death Certificate</li>\r\n 	<li>Affidavit of Heirship (Signed by a person who is not an heir)</li>\r\n 	<li>Evidence debts and taxes have been paid</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>Death of owner with a will with probate proceedings conducted in the state where the property is located</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\