ization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.\r\n<h3>Compassionate Stewardship</h3>\r\nPositively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.\r\n<h3></h3>','Who We Are','','inherit','closed','closed','','67-revision-v1','','','2016-05-04 01:53:21','2016-05-04 01:53:21','',67,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/04/67-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
