=\"http://www.energyindepth.com\">Energy In Depth</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.eia.gov\">U.S. Energy Information Administration</a></li>\r\n 	<li><a href=\"http://www.bakerhughes.com\">Baker Hughes</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Articles &amp; Publications:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The United States of Gas By: Robert Hefner</li>\r\n 	<li>The Basics: Well to Wheel By: COGA</li>\r\n 	<li>The Arc of History By: J.P. Morgan</li>\r\n</ul>','Inside Energy','','inherit','closed','closed','','212-revision-v1','','','2016-05-24 18:36:16','2016-05-24 18:36:16','',212,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/24/212-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
