	(940,2,'2016-05-31 15:53:01','2016-05-31 15:53:01','At FourPoint our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about</a> how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent privately owned exploration and production company. Based in Denver, Colorado, FourPoint also has field offices in Woodward, Oklahoma, Borger, Texas, Elk City, Oklahoma, and Shamrock, Texas. FourPoint is committed to creating value that makes a difference by living out the values that define FourPoint as an organization.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Join our team and applyÂ </a>','Join Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','218-revision-v1','','','2016-05-31 15:53:01','2016-05-31 15:53:01','',218,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/31/218-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(941,2,'2016-05-31 17:50:41','2016-05-31 17:50:41','Building on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies, you can expect the team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decisions with a sense of urgency.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nAlthough our name has changed, FourPoint Energy possesses the same passion for creating value for our shareholders, the same commitment to working âBetter, Smarter, Fasterâ, and the same dedication to community stewardship.\r\n\r\nFourPoint promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team moving across all functional areas we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and achieving our goals. Since the companyâs inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-tier equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. We consider it an honor to find and produce energy for America and have the utmost respect for the land and the opportunities it provides.\r\n\r\n<a><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Our Values:</strong></a>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Shared Vision â Creating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and enhance their quality of life.</li>\r\n 	<li>Committed Teamwork â Fostering a respectful and inclusive environment to collaborate across functions, embracing the talents of individuals and trusting one another to make the best decisions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Empowering People â Entrusting our people with responsibility and authority while making them accountable to our mission, values, and goals.</li>\r\n 	<li>Driven to Excellence â Committing to deliberate and continuous improvement and striving to be the best with passion, integrity and humility.</li>\r\n 	<li>Entrepreneurial â capturing valuable opportunities through adaptability, innovative thinking and strategic relationships.</li>\r\n 	<li>Compassionate Stewardship â positively impacting the lives of our employees, partners, landowners and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.</li>\r\n</ul>','Company Culture','','inherit','closed','closed','','221-revision-v1','','','2016-05-31 17:50:41','2016-05-31 17:50:41','',221,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/31/221-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(942,2,'2016-05-31 20:03:53','2016-05-31 20:03:53','FourPoint Energy is committed to ensuring all team members are able to enjoy a well-balanced benefit and compensation program.\r\n\r\nThe Human Resources team at FourPoint participates in and studies compensation surveys annually to ensure packages match or exceed industry standards. Setting, working toward and achieving goals are of upmost importance at FourPoint. This goal-oriented approach allows team members who make meaningful contributions to share in the success that FourPoint experiences. These goals and objectives are evaluated annually through FourPointâs Performance Review and Incentive Compensation program.\r\n\r\nIn addition to a competitive compensation and bonus program, FourPoint Energy is proud to offer its employees a comprehensive benefit program, including:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Medical Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Dental Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Vision Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Life, Short-Term and Long-Term Disability Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Additional Voluntary Life Insurance</li>\r\n 	<li>Flexible Spending Account</li>\r\n 	<li>Paid Vacation, Sick Leave and Holidays</li>\r\n 	<li>401k with Employer Match</li>\r\n 	<li>Annual Bonus Potential</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nAdditional information regarding benefits and compensation will be provided to candidates going through FourPointâs interview process.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/jobs/intro?hashed=-435679222\" target=\"_blank\">Apply to join</a> the FourPoint team.','Benefits & Compensation','','inherit','closed','closed','','224-revision-v1','','','2016-05-31 20:03:53','2016-05-31 20:03:53','',224,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/05/31/224-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
