	(965,2,'2016-05-31 20:59:51','2016-05-31 20:59:51','Building on the experience of three very successful Cordillera companies, you can expect the team at FourPoint to be deliberate and driven. We approach every day by making good decisions with a sense of urgency.\r\n\r\n<img class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-343\" src=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/fpo800x450.png\" alt=\"fpo800x450\" width=\"800\" height=\"450\" />\r\n\r\nAlthough our name has changed, FourPoint Energy possesses the same passion for creating value for our shareholders, the same commitment to working âBetter, Smarter, Fasterâ, and the same dedication to community stewardship.\r\n\r\nFourPoint promotes an opportunistic, performance-driven, and goal-oriented culture. Starting at the top with our executive management team moving across all functional areas we have a strong team-oriented approach to developing strategy, making decisions, and achieving our goals. Since the companyâs inception we have been blessed with dedicated employees, top-tier equity and debt partners, and high-quality assets to pursue investment of acquisition and drilling dollars. Our company culture focuses on creating value for shareholders with a hard-working, loyal, and technically advanced team of professionals.\r\n\r\nFourPoint is proud to partner with landowners, mineral owners, drilling companies, service companies, suppliers, gatherers, transporters, consultants, and all our constituents in the responsible development of natural resources. We value our alliance with these constituents and approach each relationship with respect and integrity. We consider it an honor to find and produce energy for America and have the utmost respect for the land and the opportunities it provides.\r\n\r\n<a><strong data-redactor-tag=\"strong\">Our Values:</strong></a>\r\n\r\n<strong>Shared Vision</strong>\r\n\r\nCreating an organization of people who share a long-term perspective driven to create value and