copy of conveyance document filed of record in the county which the property is located</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3><strong>Trust or Partnership Creation or Dissolution</strong></h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Trust or Partnership Agreement and recorded conveyance(s) (if applicable)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><em>Legal Advice</em></strong>\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is unable to provide legal advice. Please contact an attorney for any questions regarding legal advice.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>IRS Form W-9</em></strong>\r\n\r\nFederal law requires all owners to provide their social security number or tax identification number via an IRS Form <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/FourPoint_W9.pdf\" target=\"_blank\">W-9</a>. Should you fail to provide this information, you may become subject to non-refundable backup withholding.','Change of Ownership','','inherit','closed','closed','','197-revision-v1','','','2016-06-01 15:03:31','2016-06-01 15:03:31','',197,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/06/01/197-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
