	(1099,2,'2016-06-09 19:22:37','2016-06-09 19:22:37','While success in business and being the best is always at the forefront of the FourPoint organization, giving back provides the balance the team needs to remain focused. FourPoint Energy values Compassionate Stewardship and strives to positively impact the lives of employees, partners, landowners, and shareholders by caring for and about people, communities, assets and performance.\r\n\r\nThe team at FourPoint takes pride in being able to give back and make a difference in people\'s lives, not only within the communities where employees live and work, but also on a national and global level. <del data-redactor-tag=\"del\"></del>FourPoint demonstrates support and community involvement in a variety of ways, from sponsored golf tournaments, luncheons, charitable donations, adopt-a-family programs, and numerous sponsored events within their operating communities.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy believes in taking an active role for supporting local initiatives. The company is an active member of the:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Quarterly Forum</li>\r\n 	<li>Kynd Hub</li>\r\n 	<li>Canadian Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n 	<li>Wheeler Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n 	<li>Cheyenne - Roger Mills Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n 	<li>Elk City Chamber of Commerce</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<em>âWe appreciate being part of the business community in the Texas Panhandle and Western Oklahoma. Our sponsorship and volunteer support of community groups and events is a small way to show our support for the communities where we live and workâ</em> â George Solich, President &amp; CEO','Community Engagement','','inherit','closed','closed','','215-revision-v1','','','2016-06-09 19:22:37','2016-06-09 19:22:37','',215,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/06/09/215-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
	(1101,2,'2016-06-09 19:24:46','2016-06-09 19:24:46','&nbsp;\r\n\r\nAt FourPoint our industry is energy but our business is opportunity. <a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more about</a> how your opportunities can grow alongside ours.\r\n\r\nFourPoint Energy is a leading independent, privately-owned exploration and production company headquartered in Denver, Colorado. FourPoint also operates four field offices located in Elk City and Woodward, Oklahoma, and Borger and Shamrock, Texas. Our entire team is committed to creating value that makes a difference by living out the <a href=\"http://fourpointenergy.com/about/who-we-are/\">values</a> (hyperlink) that define FourPoint as an organization.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://careers-fourpointenergy.icims.com/\" target=\"_blank\">View open positions and apply</a>','Join Our Team','','inherit','closed','closed','','218-revision-v1','','','2016-06-09 19:24:46','2016-06-09 19:24:46','',218,'http://fourpointenergy.com/2016/06/09/218-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
